OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fgreyer for Friday evening with some
OL,7,Foutbreaks of light rain moving across
OL,8,Fthe region overnight. Drier again by
OL,9,Fdawn but skies remaining rather cloudy
OL,10,Ffor many, with hill and coastal fog in
OL,11,Fthe west. A mild night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FLow cloud retreating back to
OL,14,Fwestern coasts, where it may locally
OL,15,Fpersist. A dry, bright and warm day
OL,16,Ffor most inland, although sunshine may
OL,17,Fbe slightly hazy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
